					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "This is the same character as Andorn, the bandit guard within the chapel.\n\nThis character is talking to the players through a door - he's locked the door and is on the other side, so they'll be talking TO the door and can't see him.\n\nThe player is talking to a gullible bandit through a door - the bandit is inside a chapel dungeon and his friends are outside. The player has probably either killed them or scared them away at this point. The guard is not very bright..."
				}
